"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-22--Paris-is-ready-for-2024-Summer-Olympic-Games-organizers-say-1vrc8IThIsw-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Tony Estanguet, president of the Paris 2024 Organizing Committee for the Olympic and Paralympic Games, said at a press conference on Sunday that the French capital is ready for the coming Games.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 376, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9177580520880557, \"rank\": 0.0389733210508895, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are ready as we head into the final phase,\\\" Estanguet told reporters.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For as long as the closing ceremony has not finished, we need to remain vigilant.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But today we are exactly where we would have dreamed of being a few years ago.\\\"\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In his reply to CGTN Sports Scene's Greg Laffradi, Estanguet said that he's confident that the openning ceremony of the Games will be \\\"a great moment of celebration.\\\"\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9322536051694756e-20, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the predictions are very positive for the weather on next Friday,\\\" Estanguet said.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, you can be confident it will be a great moment of celebration.\\\"\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony of the 2024 Summer Olympics will take place on Friday on the River Seine, where the outdoor Olympic swimming events will happen.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the indicators for the Seine are positive at this stage,\\\" Estanguet added.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 9.097415562340669e-13, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both he and Anne Hidalgo, mayor of Paris, swam in the river last week to prove the quality of the water.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1230, \"end\": 1242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999897682, \"rank\": 1.0304104564705205e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the first Summer Olympic opening ceremony outside the main stadium, 6,000-7,000 athletes will sail down the Seine on 85 barges and boats.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 9.097415562340669e-13, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As many as 300,000 spectators are set to watch the parade from stands and on the river banks when another 200,000 will do so from the overlooking apartments.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have always tried to maintain as high a level of ambition as possible so that these Games make France shine,\\\" Estanguet said and reminded people that there are still about 4,000 tickets available for the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8028560237239952, \"rank\": 0.23549142535603604, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 45,000 members of the French security forces are set to be on duty when the opening ceremony begins.\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1880, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9177580520880557, \"rank\": 0.0389733210508895, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Estanguet made it clear that \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csecurity was the number one priority for Paris 2024.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  \\\"There is a balance to be found between top security, which is absolutely the priority,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2032, \"end\": 2042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0830325187726784e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's part of the objective to guarantee the security and to propose a fantastic celebration of the Games...\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But to have this kind of unique celebration, you also need to have a very, very strong security plan.\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's the case.\\\"\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": []}]}"